1.0.name: wordpress/dailypost
1.0.description: DailyPost is intresting theme ideal for your everyday notes and thoughts, which supports post formats and several customisation options. The theme is a special one because of it's responsive design, thus you will get the pleasure to read the post with your mobile device.
